Michael Papajohn https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Papajohn 0 Michael Papajohn (born November 7, 1964) is an American actor, stuntman and former college baseball player for the LSU Tigers baseball team. He plays Dennis Carradine in Sam Raimi's Spider-Man trilogy.
